case: X=+ve and Y=+ve
ifX>Y then Right else Down

case: X=+ve and Y=-ve
if X> (-Y) then Right else Up

case: X=-ve and Y=+ve
if -X>Y then Left else Down

case: X=-ve and Y=-ve
if -x>-Y then Left else UP

above case has been tested.

if (screenX-tx > 0 && screenY-ty>0 && screenY-ty < screenX-tx )
				tilt=1;		//right
			else
				tilt=4;
			if (tx-screenX >0 && screenY-ty>0 &&tx-screenX> screenY-ty  )
				tilt=2;
			else
				tilt=4;
			if(screenX-tx > 0 && screenY-ty<0 && ty-screenY< screenX-tx)
				tilt=1;	//right
			else
				tilt=3;
			if(tx-screenX >0 && ty-screenY>0 &&tx-screenX> ty-screenY )
				tilt=2;	//left
			else
				tilt=3;
